      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i do know people, but they just keep saying \"it gets better\" or \"hang in there\" and it honestly makes me feel more isolated. like they don't get that this isn't a bad mood, it's my actual life. every single second. when everything is just constant agony, \"staying strong\" feels like such a cruel thing to ask of someone. sometimes it feels like the only way to actually win is to just stop playing the game entirely.",
